    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing the global economy in 2026. Picture a central, glowing sphere symbolizing the world, intricately connected by a web of subtle, glowing lines representing trade routes and digital data flows. These lines are partially disrupted or re-routed, showing some paths becoming stronger (friend-shoring) while others are fragmenting. Around the sphere, abstract graphical elements like rising graphs and dynamic currents signify inflation and economic shifts. Subtle national flags (India, US, UK, Canada, Australia, China, EU) can be integrated as faint, translucent overlays on different parts of the web, indicating geopolitical influence without being overtly dominant. The overall tone should be professional, insightful, and slightly futuristic, using a rich palette of blues, greens, and subtle golds, against a dark, sophisticated background.",
