    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual and dynamic visual representing the global reach and evolving nature of the Oscars in 2026. Imagine a shimmering golden Oscar statuette at the center, surrounded by stylized, interconnected holographic projections of diverse film scenes, streaming platform logos (like Netflix, Amazon Prime Video, Apple TV+), and subtle outlines of iconic cityscapes from India (Mumbai's Gateway of India), the United States (Hollywood sign), the United Kingdom (Big Ben), Canada (CN Tower), and Australia (Sydney Opera House). The projections should subtly blend, symbolizing the convergence of traditional cinema with digital distribution and international storytelling. The overall mood is futuristic, elegant, and interconnected, with a soft, ethereal glow. A low-angle, wide shot emphasizing grandeur and global connection.",
