    { question: "How is the FIFA World Cup 2026 leveraging technology?", answer: "The tournament is extensively utilizing advanced technology such as Video Assistant Referee (VAR) and semi-automated offside technology to ensure fair play and enhance decision-making. Digital platforms are also crucial for record-breaking global viewership and fan engagement." }
