    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing the dynamic and volatile nature of crypto markets. Abstract lines and geometric shapes in gradients of green (growth), red (decline), and blue (stability/technology) intertwine, symbolizing rise and fall, interconnectedness, and global market forces. A subtle digital grid or circuit board pattern in the background, suggesting blockchain technology. Emphasize movement and interaction rather than static coins or charts. The composition should convey both risk and opportunity. Modern, sophisticated, and slightly futuristic aesthetic, suitable for a financial news article on digital asset trends. Avoid literal cryptocurrency symbols or stock chart lines.",
