      bullCase: "The bullish thesis posits that integrating Bitcoin rewards into digital Bible apps will dramatically increase engagement, particularly among younger demographics, driving substantial user growth and adoption of both the apps and Bitcoin itself. This model could create a new, sustainable revenue stream through premium subscriptions and potentially foster a sense of digital community, while also acting as a significant catalyst for mainstream crypto education and usage.",
