    investorTakeaways: ["Exercise extreme caution with AI-driven trading tools; understand that automation does not equate to guaranteed profits and carries significant risk.", "Differentiate between legitimate institutional adoption of blockchain (like bank tokenization) and highly speculative, unverified crypto projects.", "Conduct thorough due diligence on any product or service combining AI and crypto, especially those with vague claims or excessive marketing buzzwords.", "Be aware of the evolving regulatory landscape, as new rules for AI in finance and tokenized assets will impact market dynamics and investor protection.", "Consider the potential for increased market volatility as AI agents become more prevalent in trading, and diversify portfolios accordingly."],
